1
00:00:00,458 --> 00:00:03,753
I'm seeing someone right now.

2
00:00:04,462 --> 00:00:05,630
It's a bit difficult right now,

3
00:00:05,630 --> 00:00:07,966
so I'll tell you later.

4
00:00:08,425 --> 00:00:09,300
Just a second.

5
00:00:11,636 --> 00:00:14,389
Yes, I'm getting ready for work right now,

6
00:00:14,389 --> 00:00:15,724
so I'll call you back later.

7
00:00:15,724 --> 00:00:16,391
Yes.

8
00:00:16,516 --> 00:00:17,726
Yes.

9
00:00:24,107 --> 00:00:26,026
Who was it?

10
00:00:26,026 --> 00:00:29,154
It was nothing.

11
00:00:29,154 --> 00:00:30,655
Are you sure it was nothing?

12
00:00:32,449 --> 00:00:33,450
Yeah.

13
00:00:33,450 --> 00:00:35,952
It was really nothing.

14
00:00:35,952 --> 00:00:37,579
But why did you wake up so early?

15
00:00:37,787 --> 00:00:39,372
You should've slept more.

16
00:00:39,372 --> 00:00:40,540
Was I being too loud?

17
00:00:42,208 --> 00:00:43,168
Again.

18
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:44,544
Hm?

19
00:00:48,965 --> 00:00:52,635
If you have something on your mind, can't you tell me?

20
00:00:54,512 --> 00:00:57,891
It's because it's nothing for you to worry about.

21
00:00:59,434 --> 00:01:01,019
I should get going.

22
00:01:11,404 --> 00:01:12,739
I bought new bedding.

23
00:01:12,739 --> 00:01:13,615
It'll arrive today.

24
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,617
Why all of a sudden?

25
00:01:16,034 --> 00:01:18,078
You said you didn't like the gray tone.

26
00:01:20,121 --> 00:01:21,498
I just said that in passing.

27
00:01:21,498 --> 00:01:23,083
Why bother changing it?

28
00:01:23,666 --> 00:01:24,793
You said you didn't like it,

29
00:01:24,793 --> 00:01:26,169
so how could I just leave it?

30
00:01:26,503 --> 00:01:28,213
It was about time to change it anyway.

31
00:01:28,463 --> 00:01:30,965
It's always like this.

32
00:01:30,965 --> 00:01:32,592
You always...

33
00:01:32,801 --> 00:01:35,929
adjust everything just for me.

34
00:01:36,137 --> 00:01:38,014
Even to my casual remarks,

35
00:01:38,014 --> 00:01:39,891
you react so sensitively.

36
00:01:40,183 --> 00:01:42,519
If this relationship is right...

37
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:44,062
I'm not so sure anymore.

38
00:01:45,897 --> 00:01:48,399
Make sure to eat breakfast and leave the dishes.

39
00:01:48,399 --> 00:01:50,527
I'll do them when I get off work.

40
00:01:52,195 --> 00:01:53,446
Just hurry up and go.

41
00:01:53,446 --> 00:01:55,073
You'll be late.

42
00:01:58,827 --> 00:02:01,412
I'll be going now.

43
00:02:16,427 --> 00:02:21,474
How long will we be able to last?

44
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:32,569
Can't you quit smoking?

45
00:02:32,569 --> 00:02:34,404
You don't taste good when we kiss.

46
00:02:34,988 --> 00:02:39,075
This is all I can do for you.

47
00:02:55,425 --> 00:02:57,635
No, Mom.

48
00:02:57,635 --> 00:03:00,388
Why would my brother and Seo Yujun be dating?

49
00:03:00,555 --> 00:03:04,434
You must have seen it wrong.

50
00:03:04,434 --> 00:03:08,479
Did Yeonho say he's seeing someone?

51
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:10,398
Then that's a good thing.

52
00:03:11,691 --> 00:03:14,194
Don't rush him,

53
00:03:14,194 --> 00:03:15,945
and just wait for him.

54
00:03:17,447 --> 00:03:19,157
I mean,

55
00:03:19,157 --> 00:03:21,576
he's not a kid anymore.

56
00:03:21,743 --> 00:03:24,662
He knows how to take care of himself.

57
00:03:24,662 --> 00:03:26,289
Huh?

58
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:33,421
I'll call you back later.

59
00:03:33,421 --> 00:03:35,548
Hyung.

60
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,302
Do you have classes today?

61
00:03:41,512 --> 00:03:42,138
Yes.

62
00:03:44,557 --> 00:03:48,019
You must be busy writing your thesis too, right?

63
00:03:49,896 --> 00:03:50,647
Something like that.

64
00:03:52,106 --> 00:03:53,733
Was that your mother?

65
00:03:53,733 --> 00:03:55,276
Why were you talking about me and Yeonho?

66
00:03:56,361 --> 00:04:00,865
Mom seems to have a lot of questions about him lately.

67
00:04:00,865 --> 00:04:03,451
She also asked how you were doing.

68
00:04:04,994 --> 00:04:06,913
She's always been interested in you guys.

69
00:04:10,416 --> 00:04:11,584
Oh!

70
00:04:11,584 --> 00:04:15,255
Mom told me to bring you guys some side dishes.

71
00:04:15,255 --> 00:04:16,798
Can I drop by sometime soon?

72
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:18,883
Yeah.

73
00:04:21,552 --> 00:04:23,471
It's almost time for my class,

74
00:04:23,471 --> 00:04:27,100
so I'll get going first.

75
00:04:27,642 --> 00:04:29,936
That you had feelings for me...

76
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:32,814
I shouldn't have noticed.

77
00:04:33,231 --> 00:04:36,025
And that I started to have feelings for you...

78
00:04:36,025 --> 00:04:38,444
I should have pretended not to know.

79
00:04:39,028 --> 00:04:45,493
If I had, at least we could have remained good friends.

80
00:04:55,044 --> 00:04:56,546
What are you thinking so hard about?

81
00:04:58,881 --> 00:04:59,966
Sunbae.

82
00:05:01,551 --> 00:05:02,593
What?

83
00:05:02,593 --> 00:05:04,053
Did you really not know I was here?

84
00:05:05,013 --> 00:05:06,556
I had some things on my mind.

85
00:05:07,890 --> 00:05:09,434
Did you come to smoke?

86
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:11,853
Yeah.

87
00:05:12,729 --> 00:05:15,356
Someone almost stole a cigarette but stopped,

88
00:05:15,356 --> 00:05:16,858
so I thought you might need it.

89
00:05:17,108 --> 00:05:18,484
I brought it to you.

90
00:05:19,527 --> 00:05:22,030
I was going to borrow it and tell you later.

91
00:05:28,369 --> 00:05:29,620
Do you want to grab a drink after this?

92
00:05:30,288 --> 00:05:32,957
I've been so stressed over my thesis lately,

93
00:05:33,416 --> 00:05:34,584
I could really use a drink.

94
00:05:36,419 --> 00:05:37,754
Sure.

95
00:05:37,754 --> 00:05:39,756
I definitely need a drink today too.

96
00:05:42,342 --> 00:05:44,385
I feel so incompetent.

97
00:05:47,347 --> 00:05:50,391
I haven't done anything for him,

98
00:05:50,391 --> 00:05:53,311
and there's nothing I can do for him.

99
00:05:55,730 --> 00:05:58,232
We're in a relationship we can't be proud of in front of others.

100
00:06:01,444 --> 00:06:05,239
Things like this will only make it harder for Yeonho.

101
00:06:05,990 --> 00:06:08,576
But Yeonho will probably say everything is fine.

102
00:06:12,455 --> 00:06:15,666
I already know how this ends,

103
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:19,629
and that's what terrifies me.

104
00:06:26,135 --> 00:06:27,553
Are you showing off right now?

105
00:06:30,181 --> 00:06:32,683
Does this look like I'm showing off to you?

106
00:06:32,683 --> 00:06:35,853
It's just the whining of a guy with rock-bottom self-esteem.

107
00:06:38,272 --> 00:06:39,899
Then,

108
00:06:41,776 --> 00:06:42,693
do you want to come to me?

109
00:06:46,072 --> 00:06:47,156
What?

110
00:06:47,407 --> 00:06:48,491
What did you say?

111
00:06:48,783 --> 00:06:49,909
I said, come to me.

112
00:06:51,452 --> 00:06:53,955
If someone who is too much is overwhelming,

113
00:06:54,122 --> 00:06:56,833
you can just date someone who is just right.

114
00:06:56,833 --> 00:06:58,418
Well, that doesn't mean

115
00:06:58,584 --> 00:07:00,503
I'd treat you any less than he does.

116
00:07:03,923 --> 00:07:06,801
Why are you making jokes like that?

117
00:07:08,678 --> 00:07:10,847
It's not funny at all.

118
00:07:36,414 --> 00:07:38,124
Are you going to be late tonight?

119
00:07:38,124 --> 00:07:39,959
He might not come home at all.

120
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:40,751
Who is this, and

121
00:07:40,751 --> 00:07:43,880
why do you have Seo Yujun's phone?

122
00:07:46,132 --> 00:07:49,177
Someone who wants...

123
00:07:51,345 --> 00:07:53,890
to steal Seo Yujun from you.
